==Korean==
===Noun===
'''부레''' (''bure'') 
#[[w:gas bladder|gas bladder]], [[air bladder]], [[swim bladder]] (''of fish''), (''ambiguously'') [[bladder]], cf. German '''[[Blase]]'''

====Derived terms====
*부레[[끓다]] (''kkeulhda'') To get very [[angry]] 
*부레[[풀]] (''pul, pur'') [[glue]] made from the [[gas bladder]]

====Related terms====
*[[부르다]] (''bureuda'') To '''[[bulge]]''', to be '''[[full]]''' 
*[[불|불다]] (''bulda'') To '''[[blow]]''' cf. German '''[[blasen]]'''

